<hr>

##<a id='description'></a>Control Description

The organization:

<ol type="a">
  <li>Establishes usage restrictions and implementation guidance for [Assignment: organization-defined information system components] based on the potential to cause damage to the information system if used maliciously; and</li>
  <li>Authorizes, monitors, and controls the use of such components within the information system.</li>
</ol>

##<a id='supplemental'></a>Supplemental Guidance

Information system components include hardware, software, or firmware components (e.g., Voice Over Internet Protocol, mobile code, digital copiers, printers, scanners, optical devices, wireless technologies, mobile devices).
